+## Timely Anchors
+
+Use these as creative constraints when the user wants daily ideas, timely launches, or shareable experiments:
+
+- Holidays and festivals: Fourth of July, Diwali, Lunar New Year, Halloween, Pride, Earth Day, local cultural festivals
+- Seasonal shifts: first snow, monsoon, summer heat, back-to-school, daylight saving time, solstice, harvest season
+- Product and tool events: Figma Config, Apple WWDC, Google I/O, Adobe MAX, GitHub Universe, major API/model launches
+- Cultural/media moments: award shows, sports finals, album releases, film premieres, game launches, fashion weeks
+- Civic/public moments: elections, census/data releases, city marathons, transit openings, museum nights
+- Internet rituals: year-in-review, wrapped-style recaps, launch weeks, challenge months, daily creative prompts
+
+Translate each anchor into deeper material:
+
+- Ritual: countdown, reveal, gathering, parade, recap, offering, vote, pledge, critique, demo
+- Data: schedules, maps, weather, public archives, community posts, release notes, session transcripts
+- Sensory cues: light, heat, smoke, sound, crowd density, motion, texture, color systems
+- Technical angle: generative systems, plugins, live data, spatial navigation, timeline scrubbing, collaboration, exportable artifacts
